nodes.text: Toads were amphibious animals. Variants of toads were found in different worlds, including the arboreal Fevvenor toads of Veron, the grub toads of forest moon of Endor, the grate toads of Coruscant, and the spiny-collared toads of Tatooine., as well as the slow, bio-luminiscent Bo-toad of U-Tendik in the Outer Rim Territories and the freckled toads owned by Jabba Desilijic Tiure.
Zarians and Frog-dogs had been physically compared with toads. Evir Derricote was said to have a toad-like demeanor.
